# {{.ServiceName}}

Generated by `kl-go-cli` — clean architecture microservice skeleton.

## Struktur

```
cmd/api/main.go                     entry point API, graceful shutdown
{{if .HasPostgres}}cmd/migrate/main.go                 runner migration
cmd/seed/main.go                    seed data local development
{{end}}
internal/config                     env config loader
internal/domain                     entity + repository interface
internal/usecase                    business logic
internal/delivery/http              gin router, handler, middleware
{{if .HasPostgres}}
internal/repository/postgres        implementasi repository dengan Gorm/Postgres
internal/infrastructure/database    koneksi database
migrations                          SQL migration Postgres
{{else}}
internal/repository/postgres        implementasi repository in-memory
{{end}}
deployments/Dockerfile              multi-stage build
{{if .HasPostgres}}
docker-compose.yml                  service + postgres untuk local dev
{{else}}
docker-compose.yml                  service untuk local dev
{{end}}
```

## Jalanin

```bash
go mod tidy
{{if .HasPostgres}}
docker compose up -d db
make migrate-up
make seed
{{end}}
make run
# atau
make docker-up
```

Cek health check:
```bash
curl http://localhost:{{.Port}}/health
```

Contoh endpoint:
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:{{.Port}}/api/v1/examples -d '{"name":"test"}' -H "Content-Type: application/json"
curl http://localhost:{{.Port}}/api/v1/examples
```

